Package io.github.atreia108.vega.core

Class ObjectClassProfile

java.lang.Object
io.github.atreia108.vega.core.ObjectClassProfile
public final class ObjectClassProfile extends Object

A (meta-object) representation of an HLA object class. The profile of an object class is used for mapping data converters and attribute handles of the class; necessary when creating and updating an instance of the object class from an ECS entity.

Like the InteractionClassProfile, it is generated at runtime from the simulation project file and subsequently stored in the ProjectRegistry.

Since:
1.0.0
Author:
Hridyanshu Aatreya
